RES osdtriplet
! ---- RIM + SETWV / SETDENS / SSI + GO ----
RIM
SETWV 1
SETDENS 32
SSI 50
GO
! ---- MTF + MFR / IFR + GO ----
MTF
MFR 200
IFR 5
GO
! ---- PLTRMS + RMSDATA + GO ----
PLTRMS
RMSDATA WAVE
GO
! ---- ZERN_TST + SETZERNC + GO ----
ZERN_TST
SETZERNC 4..8
GO
! ---- SPDSSI + SPO + GO ----
SPDSSI 5.0
SPO
GO
! ---- GREYSPOT + SPO + GO ----
GREYSPOT 2
SPO
GO
! ---- XOFF / YOFF / VIEOFF + VIE + GO ----
! Note: VIEOVER (overlay flag) is tested standalone in gui_guards.zoa; a VIE
! that actually consumes the overlay crashes headlessly (no NEUTRAL.DAT buffer).
XOFF 10
YOFF 10
VIEOFF 0 0 0
VIE ; GO
! ---- FAN at base level → deterministic error golden ----
FAN
! ---- TFMOTION reports current focus-motion settings ----
TFMOTION
